Over the past decade, there has been a concerted effort to develop sophisticated tools to enhance the drug discovery process, such as those used in Bioinformatics, Genomics, Combinatorial Chemistry and High Throughput Screening. However, efforts to enhance Drug Development, the process which represents nearly 86% of the R&D/manufacturing spend and the hurdle on which many drugs stumble and fail to reach the market, have been minimal. Description: MobiPrimo Technologies provides mobility ecosystem technology and solutions.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, Silicon Valley, West Coast
Full Description: MobiPrimo Technologies ('Primo' Adj: 'the first', 'most essential') as the name suggests MobiPrimo has singular focus on mobility ecosystem and is committed to become the finest provider of technology and solutions in the mobility ecosystem. Mobile ecosystem is evolving at a faster pace than ever before. Just in last couple of years, a major paradigm shift has happened. * iPhone has redefined rules of game for the smart phone industry and have clearly demonstrated that software is bigger differentiator than the hardware * AppStore based distribution of mobile applications has created new avenues for third party developers as well as software companies to reach out to consumers directly * Android has made open source mobile platform a reality in so much more compelling form * Connected applications are everywhere. Social networking has become mainstream for mobile solutions * Telecom carriers are focusing on increasing ARPU with 3G penetration and newer higher speed protocols in offering such as 4G, LTE, WiMAX. Moreover, they are focusing on creating differentiation with their own branded mobile applications * Mobile phones running 1GHz+ processors are just around the corner * Enterprise customers are adopting mobility with clearly defined focus on increased productivity without compromising on security of data * NetBooks have become a reality. Kindle, iPad are creating a whole new opportunity space for multiple players. The gap between laptops and mobile phones is reducing at much higher pace * MobiPrimo team has been active part of this paradigm change. This makes MobiPrimo team unique and true value added partner in the true sense to all its customers. MobiPrimo's key focus is making sure that our customers are successful by utilizing our deep domain expertise and experience with carrier grade, enterprise class as well as consumer applications. We have impressive track record of helping our customers in defining mobility strategy, product roadmap, monetization as well market penetration strategy so that the current and future market trends are utilized in the best possible manner with reduced deployment and support cost.
